},
"attributes": ["535bda3c-a33c-410a-9805-0d95df6e68a8"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["7b408620-ebbc-4fbe-b4fd-ba7c1954625c"],
"content": "<p>What kind of person comes to a party just to drink <em>water?</em> You sound crazy!</p>",
