},
"4b2aeb83-46f8-4b69-b205-6eabd4db2b26": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["11bbd231-9fdc-48c9-9886-e0df62f064bc"],
"content": "<p>You: Did you see how much they drank?</p>",
"height": 379.0,
"outputs": ["0255b51c-c4f8-46c6-9daa-a6f86a1d6c45"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 14900.0,
"y": 11540.0
},
"4be3044e-e7a5-416d-a289-6683a492dd2d": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "bc949811-1f26-4894-b1d9-7bce4e6049d3"
}
},
"attributes": ["7a0b69fa-5447-4603-9a51-2f0e66e718e3"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>Player:<strong> </strong>I’m at a party, and someone just passed out. They drank a lot of alcohol. They’ve been slurring speech since a few minutes ago. They just stopped breathing.</p>",
"height": 401.0,
"outputs": ["66f6a02b-78af-45cf-a242-99c045f3aacd"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 300.994,
"x": 15920.0,
"y": 12060.0
},
"4da6a4dd-8b66-4577-b053-9cc3aaab4481": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "b2f11e22-aa02-4f06-969f-8b6c4724212c"
}
},
"attributes": ["6bc0609b-9e8f-445c-a308-6ed7773e6314"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["18b8d5a2-5e56-4dc7-9f9e-275ca98c3a70"],
"content": "<p>Onlooker (Liv): What do we do now?</p><p></p>",
"height": 401.0,
"outputs": ["db1890d5-ead3-41b4-86bc-f3e50142d866"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 321.0,
"x": 18580.0,
"y": 11080.0
},
"53e25832-31a9-4a2b-99cf-134eb6f488df": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"attributes": ["ef5c57b9-fa9d-4128-bc73-f87f19593303"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["10e84276-ced6-484d-9f27-022fea26c2a2"],
"content": "<p>Honestly, water could be good. Or some tea.</p>",
"height": 421.0,
"outputs": ["f8e912a9-453c-4276-a112-960103580167"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 340.987,
"x": 14060.0,
"y": 12420.0
},
