"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "bc949811-1f26-4894-b1d9-7bce4e6049d3"
}
},
"attributes": ["125944db-dd23-4dd3-ac16-8ba7cb902caf"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>Player:<strong> </strong>Chest compressions. You need to push hard into their chest.</p><p>Here, I can show you.</p>",
"height": 401.0,
"outputs": ["2516468a-ece2-4d8f-b872-fa46fb0c156a"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 381.994,
"x": 15900.0,
"y": 10680.0
},
"642a5cfc-4623-4293-8b31-c4b4351ebd70": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["64e7e1bf-ec61-4d56-ba0e-1776054607ea"],
"content": "<p>You see someone who is tired. You have to assess whether they are just sleep deprived, or actually suffering from alcohol poisoning.</p>",
"height": 161.0,
"outputs": ["39f14f95-b4cd-479a-ad36-da5e0e215661", "69b53444-9bbd-4d4a-8acc-0e168ee13306", "20da8c82-1a18-46d5-88cc-7b6b700d0e70"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": "<p>Alcoholism</p>",
"width": 301.0,
"x": 13620.0,
"y": 13960.0
},
"6831a0a4-00e4-49bf-a3b2-c210e7979b22": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"attributes": ["a865dc1a-9b84-4b89-90f4-a9a69df7a950"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["64e7e1bf-ec61-4d56-ba0e-1776054607ea", "18b8d5a2-5e56-4dc7-9f9e-275ca98c3a70"],
"content": "<p>Onlooker: Oh god, Vicky!!! You really can't keep doing this!</p>",
"height": 421.0,
"outputs": ["d69b53af-61dc-4dbc-822a-d9e2acda5a94"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 340.987,
"x": 17820.0,
"y": 14000.0
},
