}
},
"attributes": ["d485d92a-1dbf-44bb-a76b-48f2273aa8fe"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><em>I remember learning this at a summer camp once.</em></p><p>They taught you the best way to keep time was to think about  a catchy rhythm with around 100 BPM.</p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["cf63fd58-306b-4cf5-948f-048a8d2bf0e9"],
