}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["10e84276-ced6-484d-9f27-022fea26c2a2"],
"content": "<p>I had this project I wanted to get done before the party today, so I pulled an all-nighter to finish it.</p>",
"height": 420.0,
"outputs": ["c028d68d-7b86-4a90-afad-f5a32ee2c199"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 13780.0,
"y": 11780.0
},
"d359777c-a124-4604-9062-b82f9462cf9d": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"attributes": ["aa9f7796-195c-4cb4-bdd2-07a3331717b1"],
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["64e7e1bf-ec61-4d56-ba0e-1776054607ea", "0f2388d1-06d2-4ce0-82e3-120a9e57883e"],
"content": "<p>I… Drank what? I had a… one of those… cups, like 10 minutes ago.</p>",
"height": 426.0,
"outputs": ["0438034d-adb8-4b21-8920-936d7814bb4e"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 340.969,
"x": 14060.0,
"y": 14640.0
},
"d560c822-c3d4-46e6-b8d8-a5e2bc72c028": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "85e4f7b1-814f-43a4-b01d-8a1f2ab765ff"
}
},
"attributes": ["4225bace-6ec9-45cc-90b6-1ce956bdac61"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><em>Sirens approach and Vicky gets carried away by EMS. Liv goes with her. </em></p><p><em>The sounds of the sirens cause partygoers to panic and scatter. After a bit, Frank stumbles out of the house, a little tipsy. You’re still sitting on the porch.</em></p><p></p>",
"height": 401.0,
"outputs": ["1fd7db8f-df1d-40f2-ac39-9f216a0318d0"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 300.994,
"x": 18980.0,
"y": 12120.0
},
"ddc81088-660b-4114-aa9a-21996054bf4d": {
"attributes": ["195775ec-6924-4f7c-9697-ca7222ce791c"],
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["36bbd17f-850c-4d0c-bf64-17234ee3064a", "6dca6ec2-e72a-4e2d-9109-5af4a312f7c5"],
"content": "<p>Dave: Bet you’re glad you had someone there with you.</p>",
"height": 205.0,
"outputs": ["44cbe662-6e56-43a6-b639-374973bf5136"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 341.0,
"x": 11220.0,
"y": 12440.0
},
"de925341-5861-41e7-b508-897c401aa90c": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "bc949811-1f26-4894-b1d9-7bce4e6049d3"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><em>They start spitting out the alcohol and hacking and coughing on the floor.</em></p>",
"height": 321.0,
"outputs": ["727a8512-257f-4a06-a91c-da35c5f31382"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 300.994,
"x": 16360.0,
"y": 12980.0
},
