"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "bc949811-1f26-4894-b1d9-7bce4e6049d3"
}
},
"attributes": ["8786b39c-f05b-4433-b451-12a7d8480ee6"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>Player: I’m not sure exactly, but it was more than 8 shots. I’m not sure how strong the alcohol is here.</p><p></p><p></p>",
"height": 364.0,
"outputs": ["a494cf80-b297-470e-a597-7e72b38ff410"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 17300.0,
"y": 12060.0
},
"e4531320-4418-404a-b9e9-d54afef0142c": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>Now that they're feeling better, you decide to go check on the other person you saw.</p>",
"height": 334.0,
"outputs": ["3dcf3c6e-45fe-45b4-8504-6fd8cce06141"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 13800.0,
"y": 13460.0
},
"e5499f5b-b60b-4752-976a-9f257afef06a": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"attributes": ["15674c8a-fa0f-477e-9a82-7182fa20ca06"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["11bbd231-9fdc-48c9-9886-e0df62f064bc"],
"content": "<p>Onlooker: In all my years of knowing them, I’ve never seen them drink even once.</p>",
"height": 441.0,
"outputs": ["f7e721c2-f9fd-4c91-b501-92f44b983615"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 340.987,
"x": 15340.0,
"y": 11060.0
},
"e5f7f3ab-471b-42ad-b207-9b1e0035c10a": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["10e84276-ced6-484d-9f27-022fea26c2a2"],
"content": "<p>I didn’t drink anything. I don’t trust these punch bowls anyway. They always fill them with something.</p>",
"height": 461.0,
"outputs": ["2f8bd156-5047-4f39-a072-4ca4f1c81ad8"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 340.969,
"x": 13760.0,
"y": 11260.0
},
"e67886eb-87cf-495f-bc93-44f536f20392": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "bc949811-1f26-4894-b1d9-7bce4e6049d3"
}
},
"attributes": ["7d0e6038-f7f5-44de-8e86-fa7ae2e0c505"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["18b8d5a2-5e56-4dc7-9f9e-275ca98c3a70"],
"content": "<p>Onlooker: Oh god, Vicky! What the heck did you give her?!</p>",
"height": 461.0,
"outputs": ["5affff52-68fe-4664-9de4-2ba96bb316d5"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 340.987,
"x": 16820.0,
"y": 12980.0
},
"e8d059d1-ba3b-4732-a413-a0dc027ae038": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"attributes": ["bb011af7-4720-4e3c-8daf-f32ca00a677c"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["10e84276-ced6-484d-9f27-022fea26c2a2"],
"content": "<p>I…</p>",
"height": 401.0,
"outputs": ["2e92a76f-206d-4f2b-bf1c-6b404ab37981"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 340.987,
"x": 13400.0,
"y": 12460.0
},
"ebed1e6d-b16a-4b3a-8ccf-8615e6103f1c": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"attributes": ["3ab2508d-107f-4857-b4ce-a77cfa5ff018"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["0f2388d1-06d2-4ce0-82e3-120a9e57883e", "10e84276-ced6-484d-9f27-022fea26c2a2"],
"content": "<p>What the heck is this?! I told you I don't drink!</p><p>I don't think I want your help anymore.</p>",
"height": 461.0,
"outputs": ["21b8f7d0-a632-48d9-9ecc-958b9a8ccef6"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 360.994,
"x": 14460.0,
"y": 12820.0
},
"ee290ed0-dd96-4d27-b019-089731e7bec2": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["64e7e1bf-ec61-4d56-ba0e-1776054607ea", "11bbd231-9fdc-48c9-9886-e0df62f064bc"],
"content": "<p>You have to assess whether they are just sleep deprived, or actually suffering from alcohol poisoning.</p><p>Someone has just walked over.</p>",
"height": 176.0,
"outputs": ["92a6bb5f-5550-4be7-b024-d79577c483fd", "afd1784b-0f92-44d0-9dde-116c029d9274", "4772eb47-db04-462d-bfc9-c3cbb5c84fd8", "d406732e-dcc3-4dbc-90b1-17d98be33750", "f9a60e0c-735c-405e-b7c1-d2aa32ef3e09"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": "<p>Vicky</p>",
"width": 301.0,
"x": 15340.0,
"y": 14200.0
},
"ef7710b0-9aa7-4fd9-adfc-e96a4503b051": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "85e4f7b1-814f-43a4-b01d-8a1f2ab765ff"
}
},
"attributes": ["4fec1d23-1524-4827-936f-a11c863536ec"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><em>Luckily, you’re outside, so you just have to look to the right, and the house number is there. Then, look to the left, to see the street sign.</em></p><p></p>",
"height": 361.0,
"outputs": ["8ca00d21-c3f6-4948-af4c-77ae0777cd79"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 17660.0,
"y": 12540.0
},
"ef796571-a5ea-42c4-8bfb-66e184da9e82": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "bc949811-1f26-4894-b1d9-7bce4e6049d3"
}
},
"attributes": ["b9b9fb71-6b96-4059-a7bd-8973fbbd7802"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["18b8d5a2-5e56-4dc7-9f9e-275ca98c3a70"],
"content": "<p>Onlooker (Liv):<strong> </strong>I know they need to be on their back. Now what?</p>",
"height": 441.0,
"outputs": ["acef5b38-f88d-4161-b5f5-fd4795a32c83"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 340.969,
"x": 16420.0,
"y": 10580.0
},
"f0175fba-75a1-4cb2-8bc1-8551e68a70b8": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>Well that could've gone better. You can't help a person who doesn't want help, though.</p><p>A little ways away at the party, you see someone fall to the ground and start giggling.</p><p>They look exhausted.</p>",
"height": 541.0,
"outputs": ["a0d128d0-1e03-454c-902d-7131d5b1b037"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 381.0,
"x": 13480.0,
"y": 12900.0
},
"f2284647-5901-402f-9f18-96af7bcfb32e": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"attributes": ["16c44ebf-f661-4463-bb86-437168b8886c"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["64e7e1bf-ec61-4d56-ba0e-1776054607ea", "18b8d5a2-5e56-4dc7-9f9e-275ca98c3a70"],
"content": "<p>Vicky: Hrrgh… I don’t wanna… Ugh… My head… hehe… Livvy..</p>",
"height": 441.0,
"outputs": ["88942ba9-0417-478a-b6a8-1832d8a1cb39"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 340.987,
"x": 18420.0,
"y": 12960.0
},
"f252ac82-4648-4d41-89f4-04799795c0b5": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["64e7e1bf-ec61-4d56-ba0e-1776054607ea"],
"content": "<p>Based on your assessment, how will you help?</p>",
"height": 399.0,
"outputs": ["b921ec36-add9-4f71-ac75-afc80d031dbe", "61c25322-a055-4d17-9ed9-fce5bb340ccb"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 15760.0,
"y": 13980.0
},
"f4b48678-44bd-476d-965e-c6a6032f6b57": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>Your friends go to party in some side room, so you can’t find them. Now you don't anyone and it's just awkward.</p>",
"height": 381.0,
"outputs": ["c7b3d533-c867-45ac-a9dd-ad7ff72e0b75"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 340.987,
"x": 12260.0,
"y": 12780.0
},
"f565f01d-d2d5-4745-a153-4a6c9029e07b": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["10e84276-ced6-484d-9f27-022fea26c2a2", "11bbd231-9fdc-48c9-9886-e0df62f064bc"],
"content": "<p>You have to assess whether they are just sleep deprived, or actually suffering from alcohol poisoning.</p><p>Someone has just walked over.</p>",
"height": 456.0,
"outputs": ["b9ec0f4c-920b-40d9-8a6b-655a43113e72", "eb8978af-9d16-4a07-aa42-b099647553a8", "4f3160b5-e616-4a14-b91c-4ad1aa328021", "e7a8db94-3ef2-4bf4-8a15-88aa5edfea8f", "776cf067-dde7-4c84-a905-66ffab40b530"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": "<p>Decoy</p>",
"width": 300.977,
"x": 14480.0,
"y": 11860.0
},
"f8791b7e-3c53-418f-9c6f-777ae4d65a5e": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "bc949811-1f26-4894-b1d9-7bce4e6049d3"
}
},
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p><em>Vicky vomits and passes out, collapsing on the floor. Liv catches them.</em></p>",
"height": 341.0,
"outputs": ["f5d71f10-c7f0-4f8d-a036-65b81b244a41"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 300.994,
"x": 19220.0,
"y": 13500.0
},
"f8fa5ace-c61b-4b8d-9f00-d5d85e54f488": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "72d532e1-0247-4bf4-861f-1975c9dcdeed"
}
},
"attributes": ["7bd0af04-dd20-4481-b913-65704c6ecc93"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": ["10e84276-ced6-484d-9f27-022fea26c2a2", "64e7e1bf-ec61-4d56-ba0e-1776054607ea"],
"content": "<p>Suddenly, you see two people who seem very exhausted. They both appear to have trouble walking. You don't know who they are.</p><p>Who do you help?</p>",
"height": 501.0,
"outputs": ["d2fc59ec-c723-4d0b-a7aa-371e30422254", "a3b3ebce-498b-48c5-bbf8-47ce6a4d928d"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 340.987,
"x": 12680.0,
"y": 12280.0
},
"fa52f960-9711-4abf-8101-d1fe0592c7df": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "b2f11e22-aa02-4f06-969f-8b6c4724212c"
}
},
"autoHeight": true,
"components": ["18b8d5a2-5e56-4dc7-9f9e-275ca98c3a70"],
"content": "<p><em> Liv is holding Vicky steady on her side.</em></p>",
"height": 121.0,
"outputs": ["725f1f4e-2af2-4adb-960f-4a7020af7973"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 18800.0,
"y": 11720.0
},
"fabf46c1-a7ff-4460-84f4-ec89e33087e8": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "bc949811-1f26-4894-b1d9-7bce4e6049d3"
}
},
"attributes": ["f65517b9-6e5b-4d9e-a5a2-be5450f47209"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>Player: I already checked. No pulse. I have her friend giving CPR right now.</p><p></p>",
"height": 364.0,
"outputs": ["27c6c433-a0de-4114-b010-301c2a2c121f"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 301.0,
"x": 16600.0,
"y": 12060.0
},
"fac99888-f592-465d-9b89-b40d5656b804": {
"assets": {
"cover": {
"id": "bc949811-1f26-4894-b1d9-7bce4e6049d3"
}
},
"attributes": ["5e74383d-f5d7-4259-9fe8-859f8d88cc62"],
"autoHeight": false,
"components": [],
"content": "<p>Player: I’m putting her on her side so she doesn’t choke on her vomit.</p>",
"height": 321.0,
"outputs": ["06d49c33-4a4f-4140-90d3-fd7a776afa15"],
"theme": "purple",
"title": null,
"width": 300.994,
"x": 19800.0,
"y": 11680.0
},
